- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper discusses the application of quench prediction in the context of the hardware commissioning of the Large Hadron Collider. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of AI techniques for quench prediction.
